CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 1, 1956, pg. 15 reads: "Congratulations! - The popularity contest winner, Mrs. Julietta Beatty, receives congratulations from her competitor, William A. Moore. It was a battle of the sexes, sponsored by the usher board of the church. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William A. Moore shaking hands with Julietta Beatty, holding wrapped gift, standing in front of dark curtain
